  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decipher The Deck is a rule discovery puzzle game that challenges the player to deduce the abilities given to traditional playing cards. These abilities are slowly introduced throughout the game, in 70 handmade levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did I mention some cards are bombs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078190/extras/c8e5ec6da022829a31ac5e1cac340935.poster.avif?t=1748718218\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078190/extras/c8e5ec6da022829a31ac5e1cac340935.webm?t=1748718218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078190/extras/c8e5ec6da022829a31ac5e1cac340935.mp4?t=1748718218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 Campaign levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 Challenge Levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique use cases for each suit and face card</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other mechanics external to the cards themselves</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule discovery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable entirely with just a keyboard, just a mouse, or just a Xbox controller (keyboard and mouse together also works)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capsule art made by Tumbleweed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music by kummel</p>Check out my upcoming game, You Are The Code!<br>",
